# Transient mid-run checkpoint/stub files written by ci_runner.yml (FIX-G4/G6).
# These are resume markers, not completed experiment output, and must never be
# committed — a committed checkpoint file can fool the pipeline's diagnose job
# into classifying an experiment as "done" when it never actually ran.
**/_checkpoint_shard*.json
**/*_checkpoint.json
**/checkpoint_plan.json
